data.description: Truly stunning Texas Hill Country custom home pairs modern elegance with timeless charm.  This beautiful property boasts of 3 opulent bedrooms, 3 luxurious baths, a beautifully appointed office, & a spacious 3-car garage, on an oversized 1.7-acre lot with a private backyard.     The recently upgraded flooring grabs your attention upon entry & shines throughout the home with its high-gloss white finish & graceful gold accented veining.  Lofty ceilings in the living space are crowned with rustic wood beams & the majestic floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace centers the room.  Abundant natural light flows through numerous windows to illuminate the entire home.      The master retreat is a relaxing oasis, complete with a spa-inspired bathroom, featuring a luxurious soaking tub, dual vanities, an expansive wraparound walk-in shower with dual shower heads, & a generously proportioned master closet.  The back of the home unveils a light-infused secondary living space versatile enough to serve as your personal fitness zone, an over-sized second office, or a 4th bedroom, seamlessly connected to another bedroom via a Jack & Jill bathroom.      Stepping outside you will find a private sanctuary away from neighbors.  The oversized cedar-lined covered patio provides an ideal setting for year-round reading, gardening, or barbeques, while gracefully transitioning into a spacious tiled deck which expands your living space & is sure to ekove envy among your guests.      This outdoor expanse is a perfect opportunity for someone looking to add a pool & entertainment area to enhance the idealic space.  The recent home updates are a $40K+ investment in vibrant flooring along with internet & security upgrades to improve an already lavish home.    The Vintage Oaks community is sought after for its resort-styled amenities, highly-regarded schools, & proximity to the best parts of the Texas Hill Country.  Here there is something for everyone!  Chart your next adventure utilizing the 6 miles of hiking trails, 4 swimming pools, the meandering lazy river, state-of-the-art fitness centers, sports courts & fields, & a vibrant community park that hosts summertime movies.    This home supports a lifestyle defined by luxury, comfort, and thoughtful design. With its versatile layout, premium upgrades, and access to resort-caliber amenities, it's an unparalled opportunity to embrace the best that modern living has to offer. Don't miss out on the chance to make this exceptional property your own.
